# .pairmode-overrides — Sections intentionally diverged from canonical pairmode templates.
#
# Audit and sync will treat declared sections as project-owned (EXTRA) rather than
# INCONSISTENT or MISSING. Sync will never overwrite a declared override section.
#
# Format: one entry per line — <relative-file-path>:<normalised-section-key>
# Lines starting with # are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
#
# The section key is the lowercased, stripped header text.
# Examples:
#   CLAUDE.md:review checklist
#   .claude/agents/reviewer.md:checklist
#
